    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:32.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# Document Manifest Feed Structure\n\nEach document has its own manifest feed at topic `ph:v2:doc:<docId>`, owned by the document creator's signer. Each feed index points to encrypted JSON on `/bytes`.\n\n## Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"documentId\": \"doc-001\",\n  \"documentType\": \"powerhouse/budget-statement\",\n  \"latestRevision\": { \"global\": 12 },\n  \"operationBatches\": [\n    {\n      \"reference\": \"ddd444...\",\n      \"scope\": \"global\",\n      \"branch\": \"main\",\n      \"startIndex\": 0,\n      \"endIndex\": 5,\n      \"timestamp\": \"2026-04-10T12:01:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"keyframes\": [],\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-10T12:03:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n## Role\n\n- Points to a list of operation batches, each an immutable `/bytes` reference\n- `latestRevision` tracks the highest operation index per scope\n- Batches are appended, not rewritten \u2014 new operations get a new batch entry\n- Clients reconstruct full state by fetching each batch in order and replaying\n",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:32.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:32.000Z"
    }
  },
